  m_text: "Talk to the different guests to figure out who your secret lover is. You
    can ask every guest different questions in any order and how many times you want.
    Look at your letter and see if the answers you get match your love letter. OBS!
    Guests may have matching interests, so make sure to ask as many guests as possible
    before making your decision\u2026\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you're having trouble figuring
    out who is your secret lover (or don't want to read), you can go behind the room
    dividers and take a smoke. This will rule out one of the guests! You have a total
    of three puffs of your cigarette. Note that the guest who gets \u201Celiminated\u201D
    will never be your secret lover."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 4feee96cd0a2d5a4bba4d13382c0349e, type: 2}
